OL,3,CJersey gas firm working with health
OL,4,Cand safety team to improve network
OL,6,FThe head of Islands Energy Group says
OL,7,Fthe company is spending #4 million
OL,8,Fthis year on upgrading Jersey's ageing
OL,9,Fgas network to provide an "even better
OL,10,Fquality of service".
OL,12,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,13,FNews, Graeme Millar, who was appointed
OL,14,FCEO in December following the
OL,15,Fdeparture of Jo Cox, explains that
OL,16,Fdisruption to carry out gas works
OL,17,Funder roads is an unfortunate part of
OL,18,Fa wide regeneration plan.
