OL,3,CJersey gas firm working with health
OL,4,Cand safety team to improve network
OL,6,FHe adds: "People can actually see that
OL,7,Fmoney being spent, I'm afraid by the
OL,8,Froads being dug up, but that is
OL,9,Fproviding an even better quality of
OL,10,Fservice."
OL,12,FSpeaking about why there is an urgency
OL,13,Fnow to invest and improve the island's
OL,14,Fgas network, Mr Millar says: "We're
OL,15,Fconstantly working on safety,
OL,16,Freliability and greenness, and one of
OL,17,Fthe things that we do is we work with
OL,18,Fthe local Health and Safety
OL,19,FInspectorate.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
