OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1742577145
OL,3,CJersey gas firm working with health
OL,4,Cand safety team to improve network
OL,6,F"We look to match international
OL,7,Fstandards for the reliability and
OL,8,Fsafety of the network and as we do
OL,9,Fthat, we assess the quality of the
OL,10,Fnetwork and where we need to upgrade
OL,11,Fthe network, we go ahead and do it."
OL,13,FPushed on whether islanders' gas bills
OL,14,Fwould increase as a result of the
OL,15,Finfrastructure improvements, Mr Millar
OL,16,Fexplains the upgrades are being funded
OL,17,Fthrough cashflow and adds: "Prices are
OL,18,Fvery much tied to the raw feedstocks,
OL,19,Fthe price of the gas that we buy in,
OL,20,Fand clearly we're subject to global
OL,21,Fmarkets like everyone else."
