OL,4,Cand safety team to improve network
OL,6,FDespite some residents switching from
OL,7,Fgas to electricity, Mr Millar believes
OL,8,Fthere are opportunities to grow the
OL,9,Fcompany's customer base by targeting
OL,10,Fthose who still use oil as an energy
OL,11,Fsource.
OL,13,FHe hopes these islanders can be
OL,14,Fpersuaded to switch to gas, something
OL,15,Fhe says would "reduce the CO2
OL,16,Femissions by about a third".
OL,18,FHe explains: "It's not just about
OL,19,Ffolks going onto electric, gas is
OL,20,Fpotentially a transition fuel and a
OL,21,Fgood alternative to oil.
