OL,3,CJersey gas firm working with health
OL,4,Cand safety team to improve network
OL,6,F"We can actually make the gas
OL,7,Fvirtually carbon-neutral by using non-
OL,8,Ffossil fuel gases, which we're going
OL,9,Fto start doing next month."
OL,11,FMr Millar claims that "greener" gas
OL,12,Fsources like liquefied petroleum gas
OL,13,F(LPG) which Jersey imports can "give a
OL,14,Fgreat warmth to homes and people
OL,15,Fcomment that gas heating generally
OL,16,Ffeels better than some other forms of
OL,17,Fheating".
